show.description: Heartbroken after her boyfriend Neil's betrayal, Flora meets the mysterious Vittorio at a bar. Learning he's Neil's elder relative, she impulsively decides to marry him for revenge. Little does she know, Vittorio is a dangerous vampire, and his study holds a photo of a woman identical to her from eighty years ago...
